


Write a SQL query that orders the items by price.

SELECT item_name, price
FROM superstore
ORDER BY price;


Write a SQL query that shows the average price of all items

SELECT AVG(price)
FROM superstore;


Write a SQL query that shows the maximum price for an item in the Kitchen Supplies category

SELECT MAX(price) 
FROM superstore
WHERE category ='Kitchen Supplies';


Write a SQL query that shows the quanity of Memory Foam Mattresses in stock

SELECT stock_quantity, item_name
FROM superstore
WHERE item_name='Memory Foam Mattress';
